"},"last":{"wt":"Dawkins"},"first":{"wt":"Richard"},"year":{"wt":"2008"},"publisher":{"wt":"Mariner Books"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-0-618-91824-9"},"edition":{"wt":"Reprint"},"language":{"wt":"English"},"quote":{"wt":"Scientists... see the fight for evolution as only one battle in a larger war: a looming war between supernaturalism on the one side and rationality on the other."}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwA70">Dawkins, Richard (2008). <i id="mwA74">The God Delusion</i> (Reprint ed.). Mariner Books. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwA78">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwA8A"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-0-618-91824-9" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-618-91824-9" id="mwA8E">978-0-618-91824-9</a>. <q id="mwA8I">Scientists... see the fight for evolution as only one battle in a larger war: a looming war between supernaturalism on the one side and rationality on the other.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+God+Delusion&amp;rft.edition=Reprint&amp;rft.pub=Mariner+Books&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-618-91824-9&amp;rft.aulast=Dawkins&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AReason" class="Z3988" about="#mwt254" id="mwA8M"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt254" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwA8Q"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-72" id="cite_note-72"><a href="./Reason#cite_ref-72" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-72" class="mw-reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFStrauss" class="citation" about="#mwt255" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Citation","href":"